The paper discusses the potential security risks associated with the integration of IoT devices into the human body, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper touches on issues related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC), cyber-physical systems (cs.CY), software engineering (cs.SE), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
